schemaVersion: 1
id: newsletter-factory-root
name: Newsletter Factory
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  A complete newsletter OS in a directory. Fill in three placeholders (who you
  are, what the newsletter is about, your style and cadence), run the bootstrap
  prompt, and an editor-in-chief agent builds your brand voice, a 12-issue
  content calendar, drafts the launch issue, generates subject-line variants,
  and recommends a platform (Substack / Beehiiv / ConvertKit / Ghost) with
  growth-loop tactics.
entry: index.md
